title: Horror Hospital
description: Dr.Storm plans to take over the world, but first needs to test his 'guinea pig' theory out on some unsuspecting humans who arrive at the 'Horror Hospital' thinking they are going to have a great time, due to the advert in the paper, 'Hairy Holidays'. When Jason and Janet arrive, they are suspicious from the start and try to escape, but Dr.Storm (Michael Gough) has other ideas!!!
